Package fi.yussiv.squash.io

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileIO
    A class to handle writing to and reading from files.
    HuffmanFile
    Packages the constituent parts of a Huffman encoded file into one byte array.
    HuffmanParser
    Parses a Huffman encoded file from a byte array.
    HuffmanTreeEncoder
    Converts HuffmanTree to a byte array for saving to file.
    HuffmanWrapper Deprecated
    Use HuffmanFile to save raw bytes instead
